class X(val name:String)
only getter is generated for above class
class X(private name:String)
no getter now but we can access it from a public method inside of class

class X(var name:String)
both getter and setter are generated
class X(private var name:String)
no getter and setter generated but can be accessed by public methods inside of class

class X(name:String)
no getter or setter generated at all but can be accessed from a public method from a class.